#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:41
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:42
msgid "**Checks for Alphabetic and Numeric Characters**"
msgstr "**字母和数字字符的检查**"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:68
msgid ""
"Note that checks against characters mixed with any additional punctuation"
" or whitespace will evaluate to false for an alphanumeric check."
msgstr ""
"请注意，如果字符与任何额外的标点符号或空白字符混合，则字母数字检查将返回 "
"false。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:78
msgid "**More Detailed Checks for Numeric Characters**"
msgstr "**更详细的数字字符检查**"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:80
msgid ""
"There are several different but overlapping sets of numeric characters "
"that can be checked for."
msgstr "有几种不同但重叠的数字字符集合可以进行检查。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:85
msgid ""
"The ``s3.str.isdecimal`` method checks for characters used to form "
"numbers in base 10."
msgstr "``s3.str.isdecimal`` 方法用于检查构成十进制数字的字符。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:95
msgid ""
"The ``s.str.isdigit`` method is the same as ``s3.str.isdecimal`` but also"
" includes special digits, like superscripted and subscripted digits in "
"unicode."
msgstr ""
"``s.str.isdigit`` 方法与 ``s3.str.isdecimal`` 相同，但还包括特殊数字，"
"例如 Unicode 中的上标和下标数字。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:106
msgid ""
"The ``s.str.isnumeric`` method is the same as ``s3.str.isdigit`` but also"
" includes other characters that can represent quantities such as unicode "
"fractions."
msgstr ""
"``s.str.isnumeric`` 方法与 ``s3.str.isdigit`` 相同，但还包括其他可以表示"
"数量的字符，例如 Unicode 分数。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:117
msgid "**Checks for Whitespace**"
msgstr "**检查空白字符**"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:126
msgid "**Checks for Character Case**"
msgstr "**检查字符大小写**"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor._map_and_wrap.<locals>.wrapper:144
msgid ""
"The ``s5.str.istitle`` method checks for whether all words are in title "
"case (whether only the first letter of each word is capitalized). Words "
"are assumed to be as any sequence of non-numeric characters separated by "
"whitespace characters."
msgstr ""
"``s5.str.istitle`` 方法用于检查所有单词是否为首字母大写的标题格式（即每个"
"单词只有首字母大写）。单词被定义为由空白字符分隔的任意非数字字符序列。"

